snippet.title: Dev Diaries #2: Nether Sound
snippet.description: In this edition of Minecraft Dev Diaries we take a closer look, or rather listen, to the sounds of the Nether. Find out how the Nether differs from the naturalistic tones of the Overworld, the individual sounds for each biome, when we chose to use music to create a spooky atmosphere and when no music at all makes it even spookier.
